Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And I go to Page 12 of Head MRI
Then 'Diagnosis' tab is enabled and preselected
And 'Procedure/course' tab is enabled
And 'Diagnosis' dropdown is enabled

When I select 'Seizure' from 'Diagnosis' dropdown
Then 'Add classification' button is enabled
And 'Temporomesial sclerosis' radio button is enabled
And 'Focal cortical dysplasia' radio button is enabled
And 'Heterotopia' radio button is enabled
And 'Polymicrogyria' radio button is enabled
And 'Hemimegalencephaly' radio button is enabled
And 'Schizencephaly' radio button is enabled
And 'Epileptogenic tumors' radio button is enabled
And 'Gliosis' radio button is enabled
And 'Scars' radio button is enabled
And 'Cavernoma' radio button is enabled
And 'Encephalomalacia' radio button is enabled
And 'Cavernous hemangioma' radio button is enabled
And 'Sturge-Weber's syndrome' radio button is enabled
And 'Tuberous sclerosis' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Temporomesial sclerosis' radio button
Then 'Temporomesial sclerosis' radio button is selected

When I select 'Focal cortical dysplasia' radio button
Then 'Focal cortical dysplasia' radio button is selected

When I select 'Heterotopia' radio button
Then 'Heterotopia' radio button is selected

When I select 'Polymicrogyria' radio button
Then 'Polymicrogyria' radio button is selected

When I select 'Hemimegalencephaly' radio button
Then 'Hemimegalencephaly' radio button is selected

When I select 'Schizencephaly' radio button
Then 'Schizencephaly' radio button is selected

When I select 'Epileptogenic tumors' radio button
Then 'Epileptogenic tumors' radio button is selected

When I select 'Gliosis' radio button
Then 'Gliosis' radio button is selected

When I select 'Scars' radio button
Then 'Scars' radio button is selected

When I select 'Cavernoma' radio button
Then 'Cavernoma' radio button is selected

When I select 'Encephalomalacia' radio button
Then 'Encephalomalacia' radio button is selected

When I select 'Cavernous hemangioma' radio button
Then 'Cavernous hemangioma' radio button is selected

When I select 'Sturge-Weber's syndrome' radio button
Then 'Sturge-Weber's syndrome' radio button is selected

When I select 'Tuberous sclerosis' radio button
Then 'Tuberous sclerosis' radio button is selected
